# Normalize line endings. Text files are stored with LF in the repository and
# checked out with LF on every platform, so Windows checkouts stop showing the
# whole tree as "modified". Binary files are detected by `text=auto` and left
# untouched; the explicit lines below are a safety net for assets added later.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.otf binary
*.ttf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
